Class SFEEToGenericArtifactConverter

java.lang.Object
  com.collabnet.ccf.pi.sfee.v44.SFEEToGenericArtifactConverter

public class SFEEToGenericArtifactConverter
extends java.lang.Object

The artifact data from the SFEE SOAP API calls are in the ArtifactSoapDO object. This class converts the artifact data contained in the ArtifactSoapDO objects into GenericArtifact object
